                    <p class="text-sm text-[#8C7B6C]">우리은행 098-765-4321 (김철수)</p>
                    <button class="text-xs bg-[#4A4A4A] text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-sm hover:bg-slate-950 transition" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('0987654321')">복사하기</button>
